{"tid":1361794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［不合作運動］多謝巴絲連日努力，入嚟睇睇九龍塘癱鐵改善方法","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T18:50:33.000Z","uid":190836,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"89962930646fead6db7b72d3bfd2cacb493f3149","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"多謝每位巴絲嘅付出！！有見兩日嘅成效同feedback都未如理想，本來都想話唔好再搞，但既然有巴絲堅持，我地就一齊集思廣益，睇下點樣再做好啲！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆，不譴責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，我地要認清楚<span style=\"color: red;\">行動目標</span>。<br />\n隔離post都有講「請記得我哋嘅目的：<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span>，而喺港鐵搞嘅意義就係要佢交代<span style=\"color: red;\">點解當日唔閂門仲趕人落車送死</span>」<br />\n我地搞不合作運動就點都會影響市民，所以我地有責任解釋返點解我地要咁做。始終西鐵恐襲當晚，責任完全不在於市民，如果而家要由佢地去承受一啲後果，我地就一定要好好解釋。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得最重要係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">態度好</span></span>。<br />\n唔好同市民嘈！雖然一定有人惡言相向，但都係要忍，我地係想令市民支持我地架嘛，同佢嘈點爭取支持？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解釋我地嘅目的呢？我暫時諗到少少，歡迎大家補充<br />\n1. 可以派單張做文宣<br />\n2. 淨係整一大張poster等人睇到，咁就唔使逐個派<br />\n3. 帶頭盔(好似已經做緊)，上面寫嘢做文宣<br />\n4. 用口講。元朗嗰日咁恐怖，唔少人都有心理陰影，聲淚俱下都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n我地就係差在目標唔夠出咋！唔好比機會cctvb播我地擾民/大聲同市民互駡嘅場面，咁樣先有機會係成功嘅不合作運動"},{"pid":"daa62599d1209b6de38d19b817bfda5884c0bcd8","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b9e6b40105e9d4d9b30cee7ea7970ab5505c92f","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"推到聽朝出嚟嘅巴絲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05288a60de5c57f725233feb260e5607322ebd3","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c39ea20dec0294f53f998a8f2eff6689445d9c4","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"我地呢個幾月各方面都不停進步，不合作運動都一樣可以！"},{"pid":"640c1b5c8f07bdd9bb143fa8166034475b45288a","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"雖然我凌晨開post，但唔係鬼！！"},{"pid":"f8a641443b992426f638026fa80b6e9b8d09a7a0","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"認同嘅幫手推下"},{"pid":"72d6be0b1205489f9636bccc805b97f40fd5ed4b","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"269cb1e314493f60eeff7a08b5b551346ddbe2fe","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"推完就認真討論！"},{"pid":"af22b80b03db322b7450373ace0b353b14234ac4","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"成功挑戰10連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ce300526499e7c0da8a0a24d9334b9cb8da036","tid":1361794,"uid":224829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32e76c9d63acabdd624a6c4f145cb62a226a969b","tid":1361794,"uid":224829,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ab8d7b25d11c605b649e214284435ae0c95fc78","tid":1361794,"uid":190836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ce300526499e7c0da8a0a24d9334b9cb8da036","tid":1361794,"uid":224829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"我其實認同唔好搞住，但萬一有人堅持，都起碼可以做得好睇啲"},{"pid":"78c0ed9cbc43253748374bda68c4bda4a21ca8a5","tid":1361794,"uid":264097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"如果真係搞 我唔會